s=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wrg1665702578278.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wrg1665702578278.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wrg1665702578278.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wrg1665702578278\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__break_210722\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Unconditionally exit a loop initiated by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">for</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">forentity</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">forlist</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">while</span>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__topic_d69854e1_d69855e1_d69856e1\">\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__p_d69857e1_d69858e1_d69859e1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__codeblock_hkm_n5z_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">break</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__topic_d45777e1_d45778e1_d45779e1_d45780e1_d45781e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1010852e80\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__d5966e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__topic_d45782e1_d45783e1_d45784e1_d45785e1_d45786e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1010852e89\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__topic_d45787e1_d45788e1_d45789e1_d45790e1_d45791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1010852e98\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__p_d69875e1_d69876e1_d69877e1\">When used, in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">while</span> loops, flow passes to the statement immediately following the nearest <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endwhile</span> statement. This means that when a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">break</span> statement appears inside several nested loops, only the innermost loop is exited.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wrg1665702578278__p_d69878e1_d69879e1_d69880e1\">In <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">for</span> loops, a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">break</span> statement is typically used in an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">if</span> block. In this case, flow passes to the command following the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endfor</span> statement.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aek1665702559361.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>for…endfor</a><p>Define a counter-based processing loop.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mks1665702559441.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>forentity…endfor</a><p>Defines a loop that processes all the occurrences of an entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ytu1665702559145.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>forlist…endfor</a><p>Defines a loop that processes all items in an indexed list.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mca1665702559523.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>forlist/id…endfor</a><p>Defines a loop that processes all items in an associative list of paired items.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unf1665702578355.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>repeat</a><p>Define a repeat/until loop.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwa1707817649603.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>while</a><p>Define a while/endwhile loop.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533492\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533492\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "break Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Unconditionally exit a loop initiated by for , forentity , forlist , repeat , or while . break Copy Return Values None Use Allowed in all component types. Description When used, in repeat or while loops, flow passes to the statement immediately following the nearest until or endwhile statement. This means that when a break statement appears inside several nested loops, only the innermost loop is exited. In for loops, a break statement is typically used in an if block. In this case, flow passes to the command following the endfor statement. Related Links for…endfor Define a counter-based processing loop. forentity…endfor Defines a loop that processes all the occurrences of an entity. forlist…endfor Defines a loop that processes all items in an indexed list. forlist/id…endfor Defines a loop that processes all items in an associative list of paired items. repeat Define a repeat/until loop. while Define a while/endwhile loop. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}